text.tspan: Share of electricity production from renewable sources,
Percentage of electricity produced through renewable sources. This includes biomass, hydropower, solar, wind,
geothermal and marine energy. Electricity produced by nuclear sources is not included.
Data source: World Bank, Sustainable Energy for All (SE4ALL)
